# ---- validation/：仅 docs/ + 2 份行业方法论参照入库；其余测试报告留在本地磁盘 ----
validation/reports/*
!validation/reports/food-beverage/
!validation/reports/transportation/
validation/reports/food-beverage/*
validation/reports/transportation/*
