!validation/reports/transportation/transportation-methodology.html

# ---- version/：仅保留 .gitkeep 占位符让目录入库 ----
# 发布包通过 git 标签追踪；分发 zip 走 GitHub Releases（*.zip 已忽略）
version/*
!version/.gitkeep
